Methods

Image acquisition

All images of the Lepidoptera were pulled from the Global Biodiversity Information Facility (GBIF), a clearing house of collections and species information. GBIF have created an R package, rgif, that allows access to GBIFs application programming interface (API).This packages allows their records to be searchable from the command line.

library(rgbif)
